The '''flag of the [[British Leeward Islands]]''' was the flag of the [[Federation|Federal]] Colony of the Leeward Islands. It was a [[Blue Ensign]] with a [[Coat of arms of British Leeward Islands|badge]]. The colonies under the Federal Colony had their own badges from 1909. The [[List of Governors of the British Leeward Islands|Governor-in-chief of the Leeward Islands]] used a [[Union Flag]] defaced with the coat of arms.
